Ah, so the unicorn has been brought in.
Your turn is after the next one. In
other words, you're just the opening
act.\n< Man >

When you go out, I'll grant you a
glance. This might be the last stroke of
luck in your life, after all.\n< Man >
...\n< Serena >

(Luck... This is supposed to be the last
bit of luck in my life?)\n< Serena >

(Fine by me, if this is what counts as
luck. I don't care if it's the last I'll
ever have...!)\n< Serena >

(Oh, Splendor! The one I've been
searching for so desperately is now so
close...!)\n< Serena >

(Finally... I've found it! I know where
it is! All that's left is to go on
stage, receive the ring from Cecilia-
sama, and then return here!)\n< Serena >

(No more hesitation, no more fear. I
feel courage welling up from the depths
of my heart.)\n< Serena >

(Just a little longer. Just a bit more
patience. I will definitely come to save
you, Splendor...! Once more, I shall
hold you in my arms...!)\n< Serena >
...\n< Man >

sama, and follow.\n< Serena >

...Please. Just stay calm for now...
Alright, let's go!\n< Serena >
